[{"index":1,"title":"【短篇·错】","content":"&nbsp;〖阁楼省灯〗&nbsp;&nbsp;\r<br>&nbsp;写得很烂．．见谅见谅．．－－","author":"♂天使不许哭♀","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.e844f11e.71q2DFnfs1VguyO5eITv8Q&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-14 23:26","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":2,"title":"回复：【短篇·错】","content":"-1-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>公元2000年,阳光明媚.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>这是他们开学的第一天.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-2-&nbsp;\r<br>她和他,从现在开始,在某种意义上来说,有了一个共有的名字，&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>”同桌”.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-3-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>”你叫什么名字?”他笑道.一双又大又圆的眼睛特别引人注目.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>&nbsp;她不语.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>”为什么不说话呢?”依旧笑着,给人暖暖亮亮的感觉.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>”......”她干脆别过脸去.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>唉.他摇摇头.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-4-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>他是一个很漂亮的男孩.常常帮她做一些事情.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>而她总以沉默来回报他.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>同学都羡慕她.有这样一个又好看又乐于助人的同桌呢.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-5-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>他总是目光清澈.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她总是脸色苍白.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>他常常笑餍如花．&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她常常郁郁不乐．&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>没有人知道为什么．&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>也没有人想知道到为什么．&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-6-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>铃响.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>放学.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她默默的穿过马路.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>突然一道黑影闪过.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>包!&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>包不见了!&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>里面有她的书.....还有,她母亲唯一留下的遗物....&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她急了.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>突然,她看到了马路对面的他.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>这对她说来无疑是个奇迹.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-7-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>他似乎注意到了她.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她向他拼命挥手,希望能帮自己的忙.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>然惜.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>他只是向马路这边看了看.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>然后,&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>象当初的她一样,别过脸去.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她怔住.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-8-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>为什么...&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>他这样无情?一点小忙都不肯帮?&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>难道平日里的热情,都是他装出来的?&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-9-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>小偷早已没影.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>望着渐远的”母亲”,莫名地,她的心底,对他生出一种恨.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-10-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>从此,她对他更加冷漠.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>不再需要他的任何帮助.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>她只知道.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>他.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>太虚伪.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-11-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>三年来,他们不曾搭过一句话.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>哪怕是在毕业典礼同学们抱头痛哭的那个时候,也没有.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>到底是因为她的冷漠,还是他的”虚伪”?&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>无人可晓.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-12-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>关上的铁门意味着他们的这段学习生涯正式结束.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>即便是在校门口他向她到别的那一瞬间她都是恨他的.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>恨他当初的视而不见.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>恨他当初的无动于衷.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>-13-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>然而她永远都不知道,他看不见.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>然而他永远也不知道,她是哑巴.&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>-尾声-&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>2003年,他们毕业于”青海市聋哑学院”．&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>【THE&nbsp;END】&nbsp;\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>\r<br>·本故事情节纯熟虚构(自己都不太懂--)，如有不当之处，敬请谅解(毕竟是第一次写嘛&gt;&lt;)·\u0018","author":"♂天使不许哭♀","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.e844f11e.71q2DFnfs1VguyO5eITv8Q&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-14 23:26","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":3,"title":"回复：【短篇·错】","content":"啊！！竹亲！！&gt;&nbsp;&lt;","author":"〃泪雨～无双","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2596aecc.pWWt7osTeiMzedd9GCY9Qg&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-15 16:11","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":4,"title":"回复：【短篇·错】","content":"啊不> <！！LP！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！！�","author":"〃泪雨～无双","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2596aecc.pWWt7osTeiMzedd9GCY9Qg&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-15 16:11","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":5,"title":"回复：【短篇·错】","content":"LG~~!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!\r<br>\r<br>暴想你啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊～&gt;&lt;这么久米见勒~!!!","author":"♂天使不许哭♀","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.e844f11e.71q2DFnfs1VguyO5eITv8Q&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-15 20:23","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":6,"title":"回复：【短篇·错】","content":"抱&gt;&nbsp;&lt;","author":"〃泪雨～无双","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.2596aecc.pWWt7osTeiMzedd9GCY9Qg&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-15 20:32","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":7,"title":"回复：【短篇·错】","content":"亲你&gt;&lt;!!!~~~~~","author":"♂天使不许哭♀","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.e844f11e.71q2DFnfs1VguyO5eITv8Q&fr=pb","date":"2007-09-15 20:34","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":8,"title"